Comment: 0,0:00:08.21,0:00:08.21,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,=================OPE=================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.50,0:00:15.49,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I don't want nobody to get killed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.79,0:00:20.15,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I'll come and get you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.17,0:00:23.25,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I am always ready to fight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.50,0:00:29.23,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}So don't take all of the blame we were all swept away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.29,0:00:33.08,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Don't take all of the weight. You always do
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.19,0:00:36.78,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}There will always be something you cannot control
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.85,0:00:41.32,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}We will overcome. Your salvation has begun
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.82,0:00:47.11,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}No signs, no lights, such a mess all over
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.20,0:00:49.29,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Don't kill you hopes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.44,0:00:55.24,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}You make me realize who I need
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.27,0:00:57.63,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I'll be there hold on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.77,0:00:59.61,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}They'll change you somehow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.70,0:01:02.87,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}So where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:05.42,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I'll reach you by dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.44,0:01:10.59,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}The shadows appear，Illusions are born
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.36,0:01:14.56,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}The fallen angels you run with don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.68,0:01:19.17,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}It is our pain that makes us all human after all
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.19,0:01:22.12,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Torn old sepia photographs show
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.17,0:01:23.98,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Our fragile precious world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.10,0:01:27.74,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Must discard it, respond to the call
Comment: 0,0:00:08.21,0:00:08.21,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,=================OPC=================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.50,0:00:15.49,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我不願意看到有人被殺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.79,0:00:20.15,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我將來找尋你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.17,0:00:23.25,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我一直準備與它們抗爭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.50,0:00:29.23,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}所以別一個人承擔過錯 我們都在命運的洪流中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.29,0:00:33.08,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}別一個人把重任扛在肩上 你總會這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.19,0:00:36.78,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}人生不定 總會有些事你無法掌控
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.85,0:00:41.32,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}而我們會克服一切 對你的救濟已經開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.82,0:00:47.11,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}生命跡象為零 抬頭不見星光 腳下遍地混沌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.20,0:00:49.29,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}然而不要扼殺你的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.44,0:00:55.24,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}你讓我察覺到我心底所求之人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.27,0:00:57.63,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我會堅持在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.77,0:00:59.61,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}可曾幾何時你已被他們改變
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.70,0:01:02.87,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}而真正的你今在何方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:05.42,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我會在黎明前找到你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.44,0:01:10.59,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}身影浮現 幻影所生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.36,0:01:14.56,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}你所追逐的 你所不了解的墮落天使們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.68,0:01:19.17,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}畢竟我們的痛苦讓我們更像是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.19,0:01:22.12,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}被撕碎的紅褐色的照片上 所映出的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.17,0:01:23.98,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}是我們脆弱的而又美好的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.10,0:01:27.74,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}必須拋棄舊世界 響應使命的召喚
Comment: 0,0:00:02.21,0:00:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=================EDJ=================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.43,0:22:18.27,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}馴染めた白　鳥かご隅　鼓動獲たツボミも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.67,0:22:29.41,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}置き去り声　眩めた　記憶の影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.57,0:22:32.45,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I need your blood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.52,0:22:35.20,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}You read love 唱える
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.30,0:22:38.84,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\an1}足掻く　RED LIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.90,0:22:44.80,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}嗅ぎ分けた音と
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.86,0:22:47.78,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}こじ開けたReasonが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.94,0:22:50.97,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}ただ平行に並ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.92,0:22:56.62,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Come and break it down for me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.70,0:22:58.66,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}A river will flow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.97,0:23:04.96,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}KEYがない「欲しい」でも　利害鳴る鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.21,0:23:15.06,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}懺悔さえ乾いた ４拍子が　奏でた意図を辿る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.27,0:23:22.21,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}木漏れ日の赤が騒ぐ
Comment: 0,0:00:02.21,0:00:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=================EDC=================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.43,0:22:18.27,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}不變的蒼白景色 枷鎖般的鳥籠之內 花蕾獲得了新生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.67,0:22:29.41,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}你漸離漸遠的聲音 是我不敢直視的記憶影子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.52,0:22:35.20,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}高呼 {\fnDFHSMincho-W3\fs25}You read love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.30,0:22:38.84,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\an1}不斷掙扎  {\fnDFHSMincho-W3\fs25}RED LIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.90,0:22:44.80,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}感應到的聲音和
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.86,0:22:47.78,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}最終揭開的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.94,0:22:50.97,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}永遠只是不相交的平行線
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.97,0:23:04.96,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}無窮無盡的慾望 是鳴響得失的警鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.21,0:23:15.06,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}連懺悔都已枯竭 追尋著四節拍所奏響的意圖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.27,0:23:22.21,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}樹蔭下的鮮紅之光蠢蠢欲動
